flowchart TD
    Start([開始]) --> Init[初始化]
    Init --> Condition{條件成立?}
    Condition -- Yes --> Process[執行程式區塊]
    Process --> Iter[迭代更新]
    Iter --> Condition
    Condition -- No --> End([結束])

